Kendra & Alex’s Wedding Magic: Part 2! ⁠
⁠
Because one post wasn’t enough for this absolute dream of a wedding!  From the first look (aka locking eyes down the aisle) to golden hour portraits that belong in a museum—this day was a whole vibe.⁠
⁠
💬 "Photos were EVERYTHING to me, and Jenny, our wedding photographer, absolutely nailed it. She captured all the big moments, but also the tiny in-between ones that made our day feel so special. Every time I look at them, I get to relive the best day of my life all over again!" – Kendra⁠
⁠
With a mix of romantic, candid, and just straight-up fun shots, their wedding gallery is nothing short of iconic. And let’s be real—you can never have too many wedding pics. 🤍⁠
⁠
Want more? Check out their full wedding feature on the blog! Link in bio. ⁠
